                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">Unleash Your Inner Diva with Our Stunning Women's Collection. Explore Fashion that Empowers</p>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="card" style="width: 18rem; height: 31rem;">
                        <a href="/products/kids">
                            <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1356594824/photo/playful-little-girl-in-trendy-casual-wear.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=_wMy-M5ysxG_tUxDGLGnFGu15ixuqPdELPgHLmcdESc=" class="card-img-top" style="height: 25rem;"  alt="...">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">Shop Trendy and Adorable Kids' Fashion. Make Your Little Ones the Style Stars</p>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="card" style="width: 18rem; height: 31rem;">
                        <a href="/products/beauty">
                            <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1351894016/photo/makeup-palettes-with-shadows-and-concealers-make-up-products-on-beige-background.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=psw4OiJBqz8138kxoqTmSzPegGGDKdD5UjnEIrjyz7w=" class="card-img-top" style="height: 25rem;" alt="...">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">Enhance Your Beauty Regimen with Our Premium Beauty Products. Embrace Your Natural</p>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
